data.description: Don't miss this 480-acre master-planned Viera Community, Bridgewater at Viera, built by the renowned developer Lennar.This is a home of innovative design with private resort style amenities. This 2 bedroom, 2 bath home was built in 2022. It has immaculate tile flooring throughout, luxury upgrades, crown molding, an open floor plan for large gatherings, private office or den, all stainless steel appliances, hurricane impact windows up to 175 mph, plus a transferable warranty Curb appeal with impeccable landscaping and stonework.The resort style clubhouse and amenities include an oversized pool, Jacuzzi, exercise room with the latest equipment and classes, Outdoor offers pickle-ball and tennis courts, bocce ball, anthem theater for music concerts. Billiard and craft rooms too. '||chr(10)||'For information pertaining to current warranty, contact Bridgewater care Reps: Haley Van Ess at 561-851-4190, haley.vaness@lennar.com, or Katelynn Brackett 321-210-9852, katelynn.brackett@lennar.com.'||chr(10)||'A few miles from the best shopping areas. '||chr(10)||'Also, the desk in the office, NOT THE DESK ALONG THE WALL, and the table and chairs in the kitchen convey with the sale.
